                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;Hey {{{Recipient.Name}}},&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;First off, we wanted to say congratulations on taking a huge step in your personalized precision wellness journey! You&amp;rsquo;re already ahead of most by investing in yourself to truly understand how your body functions.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The genes you&amp;rsquo;re born with are the same genes you die with. So, the real difference in feeling your absolute best is how you supplement to optimize your genes&amp;rsquo; function.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You&amp;rsquo;ve done your part&amp;hellip; Now, it&amp;rsquo;s on us.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please know your order has been received&amp;mdash;our 10X Health team is already getting your Gene Test kit ready, and it&amp;rsquo;ll be shipped within the next 1-2 business days.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You will get a separate email here as soon as it&amp;rsquo;s shipped with next steps and information on what to do once you get your test kit.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the meantime, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.10xyourhealth.com/why-you-are-the-way-you-are&quot;&gt;take a look at this quick video&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;one of our co-founders filmed specifically for you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are beyond excited to be on this journey with you! It&amp;rsquo;s been amazing what this simple (yet highly effective) revolutionary test has done for so many people in the 10X community&amp;hellip; And now it&amp;rsquo;s your turn!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please let us know if you have any questions at all, our patient wellness advisors are on standby to help answer any questions you may have.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We can&amp;rsquo;t wait to get your test, provide you with your results, and talk through the best solutions for you ASAP.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To your wellness,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your 10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#c0392b;&quot;&gt;X&lt;/span&gt; Health Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Main: &lt;a href=&quot;305.682.1818&quot;&gt;305.682.1818&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Fax: 786.598.8612&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://10xhealthsystem.com&quot;&gt;10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
